    ('pcm-motivation-162', 'Best Ways to Prepare', 'Prepare for the paper you must write, not only for the chapter you enjoy studying.', 161),
    ('pcm-motivation-163', 'Best Ways to Prepare', 'Use short breaks to refresh attention, not to enter another long distraction.', 162),
    ('pcm-motivation-164', 'Best Ways to Prepare', 'Every study session should end with a quick test of what you can recall.', 163),
    ('pcm-motivation-165', 'Best Ways to Prepare', 'Practise quiz questions without notes before assuming that a chapter is complete.', 164),
